{
  "stem": "11144.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were very close to die there, because all of a sudden, one night, the Bandera, the Ukrainian group, came at night.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think, in that hospital, there was a wounded prisoner of theirs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they wanted to get that prisoner out, because they were afraid that he was going to be executed by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in order to get into that hospital, they started shooting, and they killed quite a few people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were lucky because we-- at that time, I think we lived in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they got him out, and thank God.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, we were, I think, on the top floor someplace, so they didn't get there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we stayed there until-- I think I went to school there because we went to school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you know, when the Russians came, they started with the propaganda.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they started the music in the parks, and they started dancing in the parks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember, I mean-- I think I was going there and see the young people, you know, the Jews and whatever, dancing, having-- trying to get back-- trying to get back to life.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think my uncle was-- maybe that was before the start of-- my uncle was with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember we slept on the floor in things like-- like herrings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when one turned, everybody had to turn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I think this was before we moved to Stara Huta.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was still in Mochulyanka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so life started going back to some kind-- you know, having some kind of order.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I started going back to Russian school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were there until-- until the war ended, as I said before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't have any until we got back to Lodz, to Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
